Use this one-liner to dedupe safely:

```python
def dedupe_keep_first(seq):
    seen=set()
    out=[]
    for x in seq:
        if x not in seen:
            seen.add(x)
            out.append(x)
    return out

EMBODIMENT_IMPORT_ORDER = dedupe_keep_first(EMBODIMENT_IMPORT_ORDER)
```

